column3: “I bought a gram of this in shatter form during a visit to Seattle from a rec club named American Mary.  The label read it tested in at Decarb THC 76.8%, and 0.3%CBD.  It ran my ass over!  And I loved every second of it!!  I was really high, but still very coherent and in control.  Great for people who suffer from Anxiety, Foul Moods, & Short Fuses.  I would definitely buy at every chance I get!”

“First off I love my Indica. I usually ease the pain in my knees at the end of the night by hitting the Grape. So for me to decide to try medication during the day was something new for me. I looked around the sight for the medicine I was looking for. I thought I found it in Pineapple Punch. So I tried it... I grabbed an 8th from my dispensary. Took it home. Started to try to break the buds from the limbs of the stem ...”
“Pineapplepunch does the job as a dominant strain love the aroma love the smell great strain for a sativa”
“Delicious. Happy high and was able to work on tedious computer stuff. Definitely a talkative buzz. Good stuff.”
“Great high. Smoked this strain with some friends before going out made the night more fun and enjoyable.”

“Tasty/Mouth: Prickly, juicy, piney, crisp, oaky
Aroma: neutral/clean
Results: munchy, aroused, fidgety, body high, giggly, relaxed”
“Wonderful sativa! Such a rare find for me. Energetic and yet calming. It's a very satisfying high. However, it's rough when smoking, at least the nugs I got. Still great!”
“A wonderful sativa! Such a rare find for me! Very energetic, yet calming. This strain yields a very satisfying high. Fruity but earthy. However, it hits kinda rough.”

“Tasty/Mouth: Prickly, juicy, piney, crisp, oaky
Aroma: neutral/clean
Results: munchy, aroused, fidgety, body high, giggly, relaxed”

“A fruity bud that will leave you uplifted, subtly energized, and mellowed out all at the same time. Great strain for shooting some hoops and finding that zone where you're simply doing instead of thinking.”
“Fruity and energetic yet mellow and smooth. Cannabis delight with a buzzy head change.”
“Seems like more of a Indica dominant hybrid but still very good trip.”
“Very yummy, great taste and trip”
“awesome energetic high, and a great scent. smoked with friends and had a great time. saved some for later!”
“Decent strain. Buds smells like Hawaiian punch drink. pleasant flavor, High was mid level potency.”
“bought this lovely weed at de brug coffeeshop (holland) strong weed the taste is awesome. 12 euro for 1.2 is a good price too”

“Pineapple Punch has this beautiful aroma that you just can't forget . It gives you a smooth steady uplifting buzz. I definately will buy this one again. It smells so good you wish you can taste it! lol.”

“Just smoked this strain for the first time like 10 mins ago and I am goooone, this is one of the best strains I've ever had. Literally just wanna go to the park and swing on in the swings. This has put me in such a good mood and it smells super nice too. Definitely buying more”

“Ohana Gardens 

Pineapple Punch is a new favorite. I grabbed a 1g pre-roll, which was well crafted. Smoked beautifully - very little babysitting needed. By the end of the joint thick resin could be seen seeping through the paper.

Before I finished smoking it, I could clearly feel the cerebral effects kicking in. Fifteen minutes later, I'm felt clear-headed and could feel the body effects kicking in. A half-hour late...”
“great for day time use, very clear headed high”
“Very uplifting and mellow at the same time. Very feel good high. I enjoy very much and recommend to anyone who has bad moods or insomnia.”
“Really enjoyed the flavor.  I remained focus with a lot of energy.  Not too jittery and just some dry mouth. I enjoyed this strain a lot.”
“One of the chikkest I've ever had”
“great strain mixed it in with blueberry and I was tripping tingly feeling all through my body 10/10 would recomend you must do”
“Very good mood lifter and focus for completing tasks.”
